sections.heading: Sections; supplementary to existing law
sections.text: Sections 14-1731 to 14-1740 are supplementary to existing statutes relating to cities of the metropolitan class and confer upon such cities powers not heretofore granted.SourceLaws 1971, LB 238, ยง 10.
